  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">reddit gold If you choose to upgrade to reddit gold this status will be stored on your profile along with the transaction number associated with the payment and the recipient of any gold you send Although Stripe and PayPal send us a receipt with your name and email address if you provide it we don t add that information to your account However reddit does not handle or have access to any of your payment information For questions about how this information is stored and used please read our third party partners privacy policies</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

