<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="#440685429b584902910c543:TPSaCMechanism">
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="#TPSaCMechanism"/>
  <uuid rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">440685429b584902910c543</uuid>
  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">When you contact reddit support or subscribe to one of our email newsletters, reddit may use a third party service to send you email messages. All of our email communications are opt-in only. If you do opt into one of our subscription emails, only your email address will be stored with the third party service. We will always make it easy to opt out of our subscription emails, for example, by including a 1-click unsubscribe link.</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

